    "description": "交朋友，玩卡牌，扭转规则，成为一只超级异形能量宠物的主人，在这个关于90年代的孩子的单人RPG游戏里拯救世界。在杰西来到达斯代尔小学的第一天，10岁的她意外地让大家最喜欢玩的收集卡牌游戏被禁止了，逼得孩子们只能偷偷摸摸地比拼卡牌。当游戏中的异形侵入现实世界时，麻烦出现了，杰西和朋友们必须阻止它们。<br><br>来自于屡获殊荣的独立游戏工作室Gambrinous，Guild of Dungeoneering的创造者。这是一款RPG游戏，用史诗般的收藏卡牌游戏进行战斗。Cardpocalypse带你回到90年代，那是电脑还在使用软盘的时代，人们靠阅读杂志来找电子游戏作弊码。你将探索达斯代尔小学，目标是创建杀手卡牌组来打败异形。在获得胜利的过程中，你需要交易、赚取、下注、更改规则和永久性的更改卡牌。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/904400/extras/183d602a3757ec67bdd399f5bf9a0e41.poster.avif?t=1628277385\" width=620 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/904400/extras/183d602a3757ec67bdd399f5bf9a0e41.webm?t=1628277385\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/904400/extras/183d602a3757ec67bdd399f5bf9a0e41.mp4?t=1628277385\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>成为冠军：围绕你获得的超罕见的冠军卡建立你的牌组。每个冠军都有独特的能力来定制你的牌组。第一个把对手的冠军卡的生命打成零的玩家就赢得了比赛。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/904400/extras/8b683df256115c5e6477e51dd9b65511.poster.avif?t=1628277385\" width=620 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/904400/extras/8b683df256115c5e6477e51dd9b65511.webm?t=1628277385\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/904400/extras/8b683df256115c5e6477e51dd9b65511.mp4?t=1628277385\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>走向超级：当他们的生命值减少一半时，冠军卡会进化成超级形态，造成更多攻击伤害并获得新的能量。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/904400/extras/81a2a22bf25be3b3373e7ce3f09a3031.poster.avif?t=1628277385\" width=620 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/904400/extras/81a2a22bf25be3b3373e7ce3f09a3031.webm?t=1628277385\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/904400/extras/81a2a22bf25be3b3373e7ce3f09a3031.mp4?t=1628277385\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>改变游戏：孩子们有时会使用自订规则，谁知道异形将会改变什么。在整个游戏过程中，你会选择新的规则和条件，还可以重命名你喜爱的卡牌，并使用贴纸给升级卡牌。使用超级异形能量杂志创造全新的卡牌。但是要注意，这些决定是永久性的。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/904400/extras/f13291ea3c850a1c94c8f2475047c387.poster.avif?t=1628277385\" width=620 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/904400/extras/f13291ea3c850a1c94c8f2475047c387.webm?t=1628277385\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/904400/extras/f13291ea3c850a1c94c8f2475047c387.mp4?t=1628277385\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>变得好斗：在整个学校里冒险，以破解达斯代尔小学发生的奇怪事件。完成任务可以获得用来收藏的卡牌、贴纸和糖果，你可以那它们和同学们交换。要小心，没有后援！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/904400/extras/ce518bd39d904ced12ac1ebeb38d0df0.poster.avif?t=1628277385\" width=620 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/904400/extras/ce518bd39d904ced12ac1ebeb38d0df0.webm?t=1628277385\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/904400/extras/ce518bd39d904ced12ac1ebeb38d0df0.mp4?t=1628277385\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>不能收集全套：最后，你的牌组和规则对你来说将是独一无二的。贴纸是罕见的，选择很重要，有时你必须做出艰难的决定才能获得最好的卡牌。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/904400/extras/85c9005a4f00b7fcd46883b49c8fa70b.poster.avif?t=1628277385\" width=620 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/904400/extras/85c9005a4f00b7fcd46883b49c8fa70b.webm?t=1628277385\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/904400/extras/85c9005a4f00b7fcd46883b49c8fa70b.mp4?t=1628277385\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>20世纪90年代：通过基于选择、互动描述的超酷的游戏形式，Cardpocalypse提供了变成90年代孩子的体验。呦吼！<br></li><li>现在收录Gauntlet Mode！每一次挑战都独一无二的随机关卡模式。选择您的勇士，通过前所未有的困难挑战吧。 每一场胜利可为卡组制定新卡牌，规则与奖励！您是否能连续闯关Gauntlet呢？</li></ul>",
